		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">双生猎刀鳐连续甩尾产生2道水刃，均造成<span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="442" height="287" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">每15s，双生猎刀鳐之间将产生<span color="#bfffff">连结绳</span><span>进行蓄力：蓄力时间5s，完成蓄力后两个猎刀鳐都将发射1道大型水刃，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%,50%</span><span>伤害。<br/>使用「异色猎刀鳐」的水刃可以切断</span><span color="#bfffff">连结绳支点</span><span>，双生猎刀鳐都将受到</span><span color="#ffdfbf">20%</span><span>生命值的反噬伤害。<br/>双生猎刀鳐只能一起击败，先残血的会锁</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1%</span><span>生命值，当另一只小于1%生命值后才能全部击败。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
